# The edge-ui-out/ directory is the //go:embed target for the
# Next.js static export. `make edge-ui` populates it from edge-ui/out
# after `next build`. We commit only the placeholder index.html + this
# .gitignore so `go test`/`go build` work on a fresh checkout without
# having run the make target — every other file is build output.
*
!.gitignore
!index.html
